---
import siteConfig from '../../site.config.mjs';

const title = siteConfig.title;
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<div class="absolute left-0 right-0 z-0">
	<div class="text-center mb-12 relative z-10 px-4">
		<p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-violet-600 font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">
			{title} · AI 语音艺术家展廊
		</p>
		<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight">
			用你自己的声音,
			<br class="hidden md:block" />
			带逛你的作品
		</h1>
		<p
			class="mt-5 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
		>
			录一句话,AI 克隆你的音色;之后每一张你上传的画作,
			都由「你的声音」自动讲解给来访者听。
		</p>

		<div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
			<a
				href=`${base}/upload`
				class="inline-block px-7 py-3 rounded-md bg-black text-white font-medium
                      hover:bg-violet-600 transition-all duration-300
                      text-sm md:text-base
                      transform hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
			>
				开始建我的页面 →
			</a>
			<a
				href=`${base}/artists`
				class="inline-block px-7 py-3 rounded-md border-2 border-black text-black font-medium
                      hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-all duration-300
                      text-sm md:text-base
                      transform hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
			>
				听听别人 →
			</a>
		</div>

		<p class="mt-6 text-xs text-gray-400">
			🎙️ 所有语音由 AI 合成 · 仅用艺术家本人授权样本克隆
		</p>
	</div>
</div>
